  factionName: Wolves of the den
  loreDescription: Native to the dens of the Gjerdu-forests, often stay close to
    their great mother. Lately these creatures have been setting out from their pits
    and crags to roam the Gjerdu plains more often than usual. Some even say that
    they have seen them organize into larger packs than they normally do, unsettling
    many a traveller
